@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sblbff(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin((tmp + (tmp + 0.44 * v1 + 0.40)))
    tmp = wp.exp(v2)
    v1 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.85) + 0.40) - (wp.sin(v1 + 0.50) / 0.85))
    v2 = (wp.cos(tmp) + (0.36 - v2))
    v1 = (tmp / 0.27)
    v0 = wp.cos((0.41 * wp.cos(v1 + 0.28)))
    tmp = (v2 / wp.sin((v1 + 0.22 + tmp + 0.72)))
    v0 = 0.03
    data[tid] = v0
